Package: greatientr
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Risk Points Along Environmental Gradients Using CSR and FD Indices
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Who wrote it
Maintainer: The package maintainer <seszenyi@gmail.com>
Description: greatientr uses trait based metrics to calculate FD indices (FDiv, FRic, and FEve) along with CSR proportions for each site,   to estimate points of risk along an environmental gradient. 
